## 1. Description

STEM Communication Web App: Website where STEM can connect to build projects together, collaborate and prepare for exams and study together.

### Features

- Home page: landing page, this is where he will learn what is STEMConnect, trust the company and click on one of the cards (if not registered/login, will ask him to login)
  After login, will redirect to one of those rooms/webpage:
- **Courses** в†’ вЂњJoin a course roomвЂќ: choose course to join the group for chats, video, quizes, meeting, pre-exam study
- Upload note в†’ set price/free в†’ buy/download в†’ rating.
- **Projects** в†’ вЂњJoin/Create a project teamвЂќ: Work on projects with colleagues
- **Tournaments** в†’ вЂњView upcoming competitionsвЂќ: platform where students can compete in teams for best coding/project (Post a project в†’ recruit teammates в†’ Kanban + standups)

