Build Order: Always start with a plan that will build the necessary pages/component for a certain step, then when good were gonna connect apis and services. We do that for each step, example:

1. Discover feed (/projects) with ProjectCard + filters
2. Project showcase (/projects/:id) with ProjectHeader + join button
3. Join flow (modal + pending/accepted states)
4. Create project (/projects/new) with ProjectForm
5. My projects (/projects/joined) reuse ProjectList
6. Workspace shell (/projects/:id/workspace) with empty tabs
7. ChatPanel (Socket.io)
8. KanbanBoard + TaskCard (basic version)
9. GitHubPanel + CommitsList + PullRequestsList (add FileExplorer later if needed)

